<strong>IN&#45;TEXT CITATION</strong>
<br>
<br>
When a work is listed by episode/title in the Works Cited, include in your text the episode/title 
of the work (shortened if necessary), within parentheses, immediately following the cited material.
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	&hellip;a sense of heightened emotion (&#34;Six of One&#34;).
</blockquote>
<br>
Since page numbers cannot be given to direct your reader, when referring to a specific part of a 
TV broadcast, describe the scene as accurately and concisely as possible.
